00:22:04,406 --> 00:22:06,450
NUMBER 6
FEBRUARY TO MARCH

480
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:07,951
{\an8}NUMBER 7 APRIL

481
00:22:43,528 --> 00:22:44,863
SECOND YEAR STUDENTS

482
00:22:54,664 --> 00:22:55,624
KOMI

483
00:23:02,297 --> 00:23:03,131
[music fades]

484
00:23:04,591 --> 00:23:06,885
Hello there, Komi. Good morning!

485
00:23:07,469 --> 00:23:08,387
[Komi gasping]

486
00:23:09,054 --> 00:23:12,182
GOOD MORNING

487
00:23:12,849 --> 00:23:13,725
Huh?

488
00:23:14,434 --> 00:23:15,685
